trans-unit.source: Provides an exception for read-only <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SettingsProperty" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 提供唯讀 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SettingsProperty" /> 物件的例外狀況。

trans-unit.source: This exception is thrown by the <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsBase> class when attempting to change the value of a <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyValue> that was marked as being read-only.
trans-unit.target: 所擲回這個例外狀況<xref:System.Configuration.SettingsBase>類別嘗試的值變更時<xref:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyValue>已標記為唯讀。

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyIsReadOnlyException" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 建立 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyIsReadOnlyException" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyIsReadOnlyException" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyIsReadOnlyException" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: A string containing an exception message.
trans-unit.target: 包含例外狀況訊息的字串。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyIsReadOnlyException" /> class based on a supplied parameter.
trans-unit.target: 根據提供的參數，初始化 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyIsReadOnlyException" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> object that holds the serialized object data about the exception being thrown.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> 物件，包含有關擲回之例外狀況的序列化物件資料。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext" /> object that contains contextual information about the source or destination of the serialized stream.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext" /> 物件，包含關於序列化資料流之來源或目的端的內容資訊。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyIsReadOnlyException" /> class based on the supplied parameters.

trans-unit.source: A string containing an exception message.
trans-unit.target: 包含例外狀況訊息的字串。

trans-unit.target: 做為目前例外狀況發生原因的例外狀況。
